### [2026-06-28] Known Issues / Observations
1. Prompt file paths use relative `app/prompts/...` — will break if run from wrong directory
2. No virtual environment (.venv/venv) — deps installed globally
3. auth.py prefixed as /auth but serves subpersonality/round-table/family-portrait/negotiator content (mapping mismatch)
4. All endpoints hardcoded user_id=1 — no real auth
5. get_db() async generator does `await session.close()` after yield — may cause issues

### [2026-06-28] Root Cause Found & Fixed
**Problem:** All CRUD endpoints returned 500 — `relation "journal_entries" does not exist`
**Root Cause:** `Base.metadata.create_all` in `@app.on_event("startup")` was firing, but model classes weren't imported yet. Routes use lazy imports (`from app.models.models import X` inside handlers), so at startup time `Base.metadata.tables` was empty — zero tables registered.
**Fix:** Added `import app.models.models` at module level in `main.py` before the `startup` event.
**Verification:** All 26 tables created, all API endpoints return `[]` (no data yet) instead of 500.

